meats daily increases

02:45.832 --> 02:49.969
your risks of colorectal 
cancer by 18%.

02:49.969 --> 02:53.139
I had no idea that what we 
ate affected cancer rates,

02:53.139 --> 02:55.542
but I never felt like I'd 
eaten a lot of processed meats

02:55.542 --> 02:57.544
until I realized 
that processed meat

02:57.544 --> 02:59.746
includes hotdogs, 
bacon, sausage,

02:59.746 --> 03:03.216
salami, ham, pepperoni, 
cold cuts, and Deli Slices,

03:03.216 --> 03:05.552
basically, everything 
I grew up eating.

03:05.552 --> 03:07.820
The World Health Organization 
classifies processed meat

03:07.820 --> 03:10.323
as a Group 1 carcinogen.

03:10.323 --> 03:14.894
The same group as cigarettes, 
asbestos, and plutonium.

03:14.894 --> 03:18.064
