as a Group 2 carcinogen.

03:18.064 --> 03:19.866
Was this like I'd 
essentially been smoking

03:19.866 --> 03:21.534
my entire childhood?

03:22.902 --> 03:25.071
If processed meats are labeled 
the same as cigarettes,

03:25.071 --> 03:28.675
how is even legal for kids 
to be eating this way?

03:28.675 --> 03:30.610
I thought this was 
new information

03:30.610 --> 03:35.148
but many of these studies 
had been around for 50 years.

03:35.148 --> 03:37.417
I couldn't believe I'd 
been eating processed meats

03:37.417 --> 03:40.420
virtually my entire 
life and was just now,

03:40.420 --> 03:43.089
finding out how 
dangerous they are.

03:43.089 --> 03:44.324
Why hadn't I been 
hearing about it

03:44.324 --> 03:46.092
from the American 
Cancer Society,

03:46.092 --> 03:48.628
the largest cancer 
group in the nation?

03:48.628 --> 03:50.163
When I went on their website,

03:50.163 --> 03:51.898
I was shocked to see that 
none of these information

03:51.898 --> 03:53.766
was featured on their homepage.

03:53.766 --> 03:57.103
But even more shocking, 
on their Eat Healthy page,

03:57.103 --> 04:00.873
they actually encouraged eating 
Group 1 carcinogenic foods

04:00.873 --> 04:03.009
like processed turkey 
and canned meats.

04:03.009 --> 04:05.078
This is after the World 
Health Organization

04:05.078 --> 04:08.081
reviewed over 800 
studies definitively

04:08.081 --> 04:10.183
linking processed 
meat to cancer.

