we operate from 
the disease model.

06:39.031 --> 06:42.201
We are in the business 
of treating sick people.

06:42.201 --> 06:44.270
We are not in the 
business of trying

06:44.270 --> 06:46.105
to prevent people 
from becoming sick.

06:46.105 --> 06:48.074
- When you look at 
chronic disease risk,

06:48.074 --> 06:50.009
all the things that we 
walk around worrying about.

06:50.009 --> 06:53.246
Actually, dietary 
choices trump smoking

06:53.246 --> 06:54.914
when it comes to those risks.

06:54.914 --> 06:57.817
- If I could deliver one 
message to the researchers

06:57.817 --> 07:00.319
who are looking for 
the cause of diabetes

07:00.319 --> 07:01.988
and the cause of 
clogged arteries,

07:01.988 --> 07:03.723
and the cause of 
high blood pressure,

07:03.723 --> 07:06.125
and the cause of obesity, 
I would tell them,

07:06.125 --> 07:09.428
the answer's in three words, 
