07:21.607 --> 07:23.509
- My name's Michael Abdalla.

07:23.509 --> 07:26.746
I'm from Atlanta, Georgia, 
and unfortunately,

07:26.746 --> 07:29.949
I was diagnosed about 10 
years ago with diabetes,

07:29.949 --> 07:33.319
