had two stents put in.

07:33.319 --> 07:35.588
I don't know where to 
go, I don't know what do,

07:35.588 --> 07:38.391
you just like add the options 
and you don't know what to do.

07:38.391 --> 07:40.426
You take in medicine, you 
listen to this doctor,

07:40.426 --> 07:42.995
and the cardiologist 
says, "Take this,"

07:42.995 --> 07:46.299
and the endocrinologist 
says, "Take that,"

07:46.299 --> 07:48.367
then your general 
practitioner doctor says,

07:48.367 --> 07:49.969
"You don't know 
what's going on here."

07:49.969 --> 07:52.371
It's a real challenging thing

07:53.506 --> 07:57.443
and it's something that 
you don't wanna get.

07:57.443 --> 07:58.911
You just don't wanna get it.

07:58.911 --> 08:01.080
- [Kip] Government and media 
almost exclusively blame

08:01.080 --> 08:04.884
lack of exercise and sugary 
foods as a cause of diabetes.

08:04.884 --> 08:06.552
But I wanted to talk 
with an actual expert

08:06.552 --> 08:08.688
on the role of diet in diabetes.

08:08.688 --> 08:10.056
I went to speak with 
premier physician,

08:10.056 --> 08:13.793
diabetes expert, and 
researcher, Dr. Neal Barnard.

08:13.793 --> 08:17.396
What role does sugar 
play in causing diabetes?

08:17.396 --> 08:18.598
- Drive me crazy.

08:18.598 --> 08:21.000
Diabetes is not and 
never was caused

08:21.000 --> 08:23.836
by eating a high 
carbohydrate diet

08:23.836 --> 08:25.371
and it's not caused 
by eating sugar.

08:25.371 --> 08:27.306
The cause of diabetes is a diet

08:27.306 --> 08:29.876
that builds up the amount 
of fat into the blood.

08:29.876 --> 08:33.145
I'm talking about a typical 
meat-based, animal-based diet.

08:33.145 --> 08:35.581
You can look into the muscle 
cells of the human body

08:35.581 --> 08:38.083
and you find they're building 
up tiny particles of fat

08:38.083 --> 08:40.385
which is causing 
insulin resistance.

08:40.385 --> 08:42.221
What that means is the sugar

08:42.221 --> 08:44.457
that is naturally from the 
foods that you're eating

08:44.457 --> 08:46.525
can't get into the 
cells where it belongs.

08:46.525 --> 08:49.095
It builds up in the blood 
and that's diabetes.

08:49.095 --> 08:50.329
- [Kip] I had never 
heard that meat

08:50.329 --> 08:52.164
was associated with 
causing diabetes.

08:52.164 --> 08:54.934
We had always been told that 
sugar and obesity caused it.

08:54.934 --> 08:56.402
Renowned weight loss 
bariatric surgeon,

08:56.402 --> 08:58.538
Dr. Garth Davis, though agreed.

08:58.538 --> 09:00.439
- Everyone thinks that you 
diabetic because of carbs,

09:00.439 --> 09:03.676
did a huge study and that 
epic study, 500,000 people.

09:03.676 --> 09:06.512
Carbs consumption was 
inversely related to diabetes.

09:06.512 --> 09:08.481
In other words, the more 
carbs they wanna to eat,

09:08.481 --> 09:12.351
the less diabetes they had but 
meat was strongly correlated.

09:12.351 --> 09:13.619
Get that aha moment.

09:13.619 --> 09:15.855
The starches, the 
carbs are good for you.

09:15.855 --> 09:17.323
They're not bad for you.

09:17.323 --> 09:20.459
This idea that carbs make you 
fat is utterly ridiculous.

09:20.459 --> 09:23.629
Carbs cannot make you 
fat in and of themselves.

09:23.629 --> 09:26.065
We have storage in our muscles

09:26.065 --> 09:28.301
and in our liver for 
carbs called glycogen.

09:28.301 --> 09:31.137
So, when we eat carbs, we 
either store it or we burn it.

09:31.137 --> 09:33.606
Now, eat fat that goes 
straight to you fat.

09:33.606 --> 09:36.375
Your body can't turn 
those carbs into fat

09:36.375 --> 09:38.577
unless you're really 
overdoing your calories.

09:38.577 --> 09:40.313
Basically, it's 
a death sentence.

09:40.313 --> 09:42.248
You're at much higher 
risk of getting cancer.

09:42.248 --> 09:44.483
You're almost certainly 
gonna get diabetes.

09:44.483 --> 09:45.985
No one wants to fat shame

09:45.985 --> 09:47.753
and we all want everybody to 
be comfortable with our bodies

09:47.753 --> 09:49.422
but this movement to be 
comfortable with our bodies

09:49.422 --> 09:51.324
has made us comfortable 
with being sick

09:51.324 --> 09:52.892
and that's a huge problem.

09:52.892 --> 09:54.627
I go into the hospital 
and I look around me,

09:54.627 --> 09:56.963
people on dialysis, 
all these sick people

09:56.963 --> 09:58.631
and just about every 
disease in there

09:58.631 --> 10:00.433
is because of what 
people are eating.

10:00.433 --> 10:03.669
- Here's the thing, if 
I eat a sugary cookie,

10:03.669 --> 10:06.038
the sugar lures you in 
like the Trojan Horse

10:06.038 --> 10:07.873
but waiting inside that cookie

10:07.873 --> 10:10.476
is a huge load of 
butter or shortening

10:10.476 --> 10:11.711
and that's what fattens you up.

10:11.711 --> 10:13.679
That's the part that 
leads to the diabetes.

10:13.679 --> 10:15.848
It's the fatty foods, not 
really so much the sugar.

10:15.848 --> 10:17.350
- It's not that 
sugar's good for you.

10:17.350 --> 10:19.652
There's no nutrients in 
it, it's excess calories,

10:19.652 --> 10:20.786
but when you eat sugar,

10:20.786 --> 10:22.655
you don't get 
inflammation right away.

10:22.655 --> 10:24.623
When you eat sugar, 
you're not getting plaques

10:24.623 --> 10:26.125
forming in your vessels.

10:26.125 --> 10:28.027
When you're eating sugar, 
your body's gonna store

10:28.027 --> 10:31.697
most of it as glycogen 
or burn it as calories.

10:31.697 --> 10:35.568
So, this focus on sugar 
has taken all the focus off

10:35.568 --> 10:39.772
meat, dairy, eggs, 
pork, turkey, chicken.

10:39.772 --> 10:41.574
- People need to understand.

10:41.574 --> 10:43.476
If their gets diabetes,

10:43.476 --> 10:46.912
you've just take 19 years 
off their life span.

10:46.912 --> 10:48.948
We're talking life and death.

10:48.948 --> 10:50.416
- I realized, there 
was so much more

10:50.416 --> 10:52.852
about diet and disease 
that I hadn't ever learned.

10:52.852 --> 10:54.286
It felt as if this information

10:54.286 --> 10:56.022
had been practically withheld.

10:56.022 --> 10:57.857
Processed meat causes cancer.

10:57.857 --> 11:00.259
Sugar doesn't cause diabetes.

11:00.259 --> 11:02.428
I had doubt about the claims 
these doctors are making

11:02.428 --> 11:04.764
so I did some 
searching on my own.

