that I know all the benefits

01:26:00.321 --> 01:26:02.790
and now that I know how 
it feels to be vegan.

01:26:02.790 --> 01:26:04.726
- Every aspect of my 
life has been improved

01:26:04.726 --> 01:26:06.828
by adopting this lifestyle.

01:26:06.828 --> 01:26:09.631
I feel better, I perform 
better athletically,

01:26:09.631 --> 01:26:12.667
I sleep better, my energy 
with my kids is better,

01:26:12.667 --> 01:26:15.303
my focus at work is better, 
everything is better.

01:26:15.303 --> 01:26:17.572
My skin cleared 
up, cut myself trim

01:26:17.572 --> 01:26:19.908
for nine years now doing this.

01:26:19.908 --> 01:26:22.243
All I can tell 
you is that I felt

01:26:22.243 --> 01:26:26.581
and I continue to feel better 
than I ever felt before.

01:26:26.581 --> 01:26:28.383
My friend, Jason Lester 
and I were the first people

01:26:28.383 --> 01:26:31.786
to do this challenge 
called EPIC5

01:26:31.786 --> 01:26:33.788
which entail doing five ironmans

01:26:33.788 --> 01:26:36.491
on five Hawaiian 
islands in our group.

01:26:36.491 --> 01:26:38.459
An ironman is a 2.4-mile swim

01:26:38.459 --> 01:26:40.461
followed by 112-mile bike,

01:26:40.461 --> 01:26:44.465
and then running a marathon, 
26.2 miles after that.

01:26:44.465 --> 01:26:45.967
So, we did five 
of those in a row

01:26:45.967 --> 01:26:49.470
on five different islands 
and in little under a week.

01:26:49.470 --> 01:26:50.605
- Yeah, you almost die?

01:26:50.605 --> 01:26:52.340
- Yeah, die.

01:26:52.340 --> 01:26:53.541
- So, I guess the 
famous question,

01:26:53.541 --> 01:26:55.310
where did you get your 
protein? (mumbles)

01:26:55.310 --> 01:26:59.314
- (laughs) From plants.

01:26:59.314 --> 01:27:01.215
- [Kip] Like so many people, 
I was looking for excuses

01:27:01.215 --> 01:27:03.885
not to change my diet 
but once I finally did,

01:27:03.885 --> 01:27:05.420
I felt liberated.

01:27:05.420 --> 01:27:07.789
Within days, I could feel the 
blood running through my veins

01:27:07.789 --> 01:27:09.190
with a new vitality.

01:27:09.190 --> 01:27:10.925
Within weeks, I felt 
a transformation

01:27:10.925 --> 01:27:13.328
throughout my entire 
body and mind.

01:27:13.328 --> 01:27:16.564
Not only could I survive on a 
purely plant-based vegan diet,

01:27:16.564 --> 01:27:19.100
I could thrive, I felt amazing.

01:27:19.100 --> 01:27:22.070
I competed my first 
marathon in six years

01:27:22.070 --> 01:27:23.304
training half the amount

01:27:23.304 --> 01:27:25.873
and beat my personal 
record by 23 minutes.

01:27:25.873 --> 01:27:29.143
Less than a month later, I 
did my first full ironman.

01:27:29.143 --> 01:27:30.545
Although I could 
possibly get away

01:27:30.545 --> 01:27:32.280
with eating a little 
bit of meat and dairy

01:27:32.280 --> 01:27:34.415
without ill effects 
to my personal health,

01:27:34.415 --> 01:27:36.351
I could no longer willingly 
support an industry

01:27:36.351 --> 01:27:39.020
I knew was causing so much 
suffering to communities,

01:27:39.020 --> 01:27:41.823
families, and all 
life on the planet.

01:27:41.823 --> 01:27:45.126
A whole new world opened 
up, I felt whole again,

01:27:45.126 --> 01:27:47.862
connected to a greater 
sense of what true health is

01:27:47.862 --> 01:27:50.298
and where true health 
doesn't end with me

01:27:50.298 --> 01:27:51.866
but begins with us.

01:27:53.501 --> 01:27:55.903
- If people adopted 
a plant-based diet,

01:27:55.903 --> 01:28:00.842
the changes we would see 
in our individual health,

01:28:00.842 --> 01:28:02.810
in our national 
health situation,

01:28:02.810 --> 01:28:06.047
and in this physical 
environmental world we live in

01:28:06.047 --> 01:28:08.316
would be so profound.

01:28:08.316 --> 01:28:11.019
- I mean, today, you can say,

01:28:11.019 --> 01:28:13.054
"I'm not gonna eat 
that stuff anymore.

01:28:13.054 --> 01:28:16.691
"It's one thing that I 
can do myself personally

01:28:16.691 --> 01:28:18.092
"to make a difference."

01:28:18.092 --> 01:28:19.627
- It will give you a 
greater sense of well-being

01:28:19.627 --> 01:28:22.030
and happiness when 
you know that one,

01:28:22.030 --> 01:28:23.698
you're not destroying 
your health

01:28:23.698 --> 01:28:24.932
every time you sit down to eat,

01:28:24.932 --> 01:28:26.668
you're not promoting cruelty,

01:28:26.668 --> 01:28:28.302
and you're not 
damaging the Earth.

01:28:28.302 --> 01:28:30.171
- I don't want my gains 
to be at the detriment

01:28:30.171 --> 01:28:31.706
of the planet of other things

01:28:31.706 --> 01:28:33.641
and yet, I'm not 
weaker, I'm stronger.

01:28:33.641 --> 01:28:34.909
That's the beauty of it.

01:28:34.909 --> 01:28:36.144
When you all twist and 
when you make choices

01:28:36.144 --> 01:28:37.912
for the great good of 
others, it comes around,

01:28:37.912 --> 01:28:39.781
benefits as well, 
benefits us all.

01:28:39.781 --> 01:28:42.150
- Studies show that 
we cannot only survive

01:28:42.150 --> 01:28:43.384
but we can thrive.

01:28:43.384 --> 01:28:45.987
- I just feel this is 
a great way to live.

01:28:45.987 --> 01:28:47.622
Not harm the other beings

01:28:47.622 --> 01:28:49.924
when we can be 
healthy and happier.

01:28:49.924 --> 01:28:52.860
I love it, it's a great life.

01:28:52.860 --> 01:28:56.097
- I never thought that I could 
feel this good at this age

01:28:56.097 --> 01:28:58.433
and I just want everybody 
to feel this way.

01:28:58.433 --> 01:29:01.202
I feel like a 20-year-old, 
I'm almost 50.

01:29:01.202 --> 01:29:04.839
- Nothing tastes as good as 
health, it feels basically.

01:29:04.839 --> 01:29:07.108
- And so, the choices that 
we make every single day,

01:29:07.108 --> 01:29:09.310
day in and day out 
around our food

01:29:09.310 --> 01:29:13.448
has the capacity to bring us 
true health, optimal wellness,

01:29:13.448 --> 01:29:16.150
not just individually 
but collectively

01:29:16.150 --> 01:29:18.586
as species and for our planet.

01:29:18.586 --> 01:29:20.922
- We're not gonna live forever

01:29:20.922 --> 01:29:23.491
but while we are alive, 
we can live well.

01:29:23.491 --> 01:29:26.027
And, for me, as a doctor, 
that's what I wanna see.

01:29:26.027 --> 01:29:29.697
- Where there's a 
will, there is a way,

01:29:29.697 --> 01:29:31.265
and I believe that.

